{"tid":2086304,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。","createTime":"2020-06-30T08:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T09:08:41.000Z","uid":14918,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"abc9a72bf61f746f8b705930d0d5dd650d095a83","tid":2086304,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:42:48.000Z","msg":"「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」<br />\n<br />\n「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眾志關門大吉，龍門退出 又有咩好怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n信念依然係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a60e4facf9928b8405d9f649b3a3f3aa6a9014","tid":2086304,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:44:26.000Z","msg":"咁快有一個負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521daa2d1acbc664c8cbdabae9bfa032a740787e","tid":2086304,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:44:57.000Z","msg":"岩 港豬就算個個移民入集中營或者入黨<br />\n信念都會係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4845b34b5be67c7bb027a6b3b375a82e6e67558a","tid":2086304,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"521daa2d1acbc664c8cbdabae9bfa032a740787e","tid":2086304,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:44:57.000Z","msg":"岩 港豬就算個個移民入集中營或者入黨<br />\n信念都會係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:49:15.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無限上綱"},{"pid":"004137a19b2e59d7bfaf2bb1ff289a2ec9bf018c","tid":2086304,"uid":312736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:52:24.000Z","msg":"啱<br />\n就算佢哋係咁打壓我哋都好<br />\n都改變唔到我哋嘅思